WEBVTT

00:04:28.307 --> 00:04:30.212
Yurak jarrohlaridan farqli o’laroq,

00:04:30.236 --> 00:04:32.938
men ularni hozir,
shu yerda ko’rsata olaman.

00:04:32.962 --> 00:04:36.022
Demak, masalan, sur’atchi hozir bu yerda,

00:04:36.046 --> 00:04:38.103
lampalar esa u yerda va mijoz menga:

00:04:38.127 --> 00:04:40.274
“Bizga, ko’chada
ketyatgan sur'at kerak” desa,

00:04:40.298 --> 00:04:43.982
shunda bu oyoq cho’zilgan holda
oldinga yuradi, bu qo’l orqaga,

00:04:44.006 --> 00:04:46.924
buni esa oldinga,
boshing sal chetga va ketdi,

00:04:46.948 --> 00:04:49.948
oldinga-orqaga, orqadigi
hayolingdagi do’stlaringa qarab…

00:04:49.972 --> 00:04:51.691
300, 400, 500 marta.

00:04:51.715 --> 00:04:53.395
(Kulgi)

00:04:53.419 --> 00:04:55.206
Va bu shunday ko’rinishi mumkin.

00:04:55.230 --> 00:04:57.417
(Kulgi)

00:04:57.441 --> 00:05:00.369
Umid qilamanki, o’rtadagi
rasmdan yaxshiroq,